%F A024067 a(n) = 12*a(n-1) - 51*a(n-2) + 110*a(n-3) - 135*a(n-4) + 96*a(n-5) - 37*a(n-6) + 6*a(n-7); a(0)=1, a(1)=5, a(2)=4, a(3)=-27, a(4)=272, a(5)=4651, a(6)=38880. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Apr 08 2015
%F A024067 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Jun 01 2026: (Start)
%F A024067 G.f.: (1 - 7*x - 5*x^2 + 70*x^3 + 385*x^4 + 149*x^5 + 7*x^6)/((1-6*x)*(x-1)^6).
%F A024067 E.g.f.: exp(6*x) - x*exp(x)*(1 + 15*x + 25*x^2 + 10*x^3 + x^4).
%F A024067 a(n) = A000400(n) - A000584(n). (End)
